:::'''Ulysse:''' Remember this and tell everyone &mdash; The eldest son of House Mentes of Odressian, holder of the Titan Medal, and a noble who's determined to lead the people forward &mdash; Ulysse Mentes, offered you a helping hand under the gaze of Kephale.
